headline: Raymond James Financial Ties AI And Acquisition Push To Advisor Growth
summary: Raymond James Financial (NYSE:RJF) has agreed to acquire Clark Capital Management, expanding its asset management capabilities. The firm continues to recruit new financial advisor teams, adding to its wealth management platform. Raymond James has also introduced a proprietary AI operations agent designed to support financial advisors.
